# ── App ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ENVIRONMENT=production
HOST=0.0.0.0
PORT=8000                          # Railway overrides this automatically
ALLOWED_ORIGIN=https://YOUR_VERCEL_APP.vercel.app

# ── OpenAI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
OPENAI_EMBEDDINGS_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small

# ── Supabase REST API (preferred — works over HTTPS everywhere) ───────────────
SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=sb_secret_...         # Project Settings → API → service_role key

# ── Supabase Direct Postgres (optional fallback) ──────────────────────────────
# DB_URL=postgresql://postgres:PASSWORD@db.YOUR_REF.supabase.co:5432/postgres

# ── SQLite (local dev only — ignored when SUPABASE_KEY is set) ───────────────
DB_PATH=app/data/app.db

# ── n8n (optional outbound trigger) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Use /webhook-test/... only while testing in n8n. Replace with /webhook/... for
# the live workflow once it is active.
N8N_WEBHOOK_URL=https://YOUR_N8N_HOST/webhook/YOUR_WORKFLOW_ID

# ── OpenStates (state legislation search) ──────────────────────────────────────
# Register for a free key at https://openstates.org/accounts/login/
# Add this to Railway environment variables for production.
OPENSTATES_API_KEY=your_openstates_api_key_here
